#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "thag1.25:4.1"
msgid "1.25. Nandiyattheragāthā"
msgstr "1.25. Nandiya"

#. </h1></div><blockquote class="gatha"><p><a class="sc" id="1"></a><a
#. class="vns" id="vns25"></a><a class="vnp" id="vnp25"></a>
msgctxt "thag1.25:5.1"
msgid "“Obhāsajātaṃ phalagaṃ,"
msgstr "Dark One, after attacking such a monk—"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag1.25:5.2"
msgid "cittaṃ yassa abhiṇhaso;"
msgstr "one who has arrived at the fruit,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag1.25:5.3"
msgid "Tādisaṃ bhikkhumāsajja,"
msgstr "and whose mind is always full of light—"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag1.25:5.4"
msgid "kaṇha dukkhaṃ nigacchasī”ti."
msgstr "you’ll fall into suffering."

#. </p></blockquote><p class="endsutta">
